OL,3,CWhat is a 'super plume' summer which
OL,4,Ccould push temperatures to 40C?
OL,6,FAfter the warmest spring on record and
OL,7,Fa sizzling Summer Solstice that
OL,8,Fbrought 33C heat on Saturday, it's
OL,9,Fstarting to look like 2025 is anything
OL,10,Fbut average on the weather front.
OL,12,FThis week brings a bit of a breather
OL,13,Fwith cool Atlantic air making things
OL,14,Ffeel fresher and keeping temperatures
OL,15,Fa little lower.
OL,17,FThere will be passing showers at
OL,18,Ftimes, but any sunshine will quickly
OL,19,Fbump temperatures back into the mid-
OL,20,F20s, especially in the southeast,
OL,21,Fwhere highs of 25-28C are possible.
