OL,3,CWhat is a 'super plume' summer which
OL,4,Ccould push temperatures to 40C?
OL,6,FEarly signals suggest another heat
OL,7,Fsurge could arrive by the second half
OL,8,Fof next weekend with highs close to
OL,9,F30C or more by next Monday, just in
OL,10,Ftime for the start of Wimbledon.
OL,12,FThat would mark the third 30C+ this
OL,13,Fmonth, the kind of repeat heat which
OL,14,Fhints at a 'super plume' summer
OL,15,Funfolding.
OL,17,FWhat is a 'super plume' summer?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
