OL,3,CWhat is a 'super plume' summer which
OL,4,Ccould push temperatures to 40C?
OL,6,FThis year, the position of the jet
OL,7,Fstream means we're more susceptible to
OL,8,Fhot, humid plumes of air from Europe.
OL,10,FIt's not a consistent feature, but it
OL,11,Fmeans higher temperatures have a
OL,12,Fhigher chance of returning throughout
OL,13,Fthe coming weeks.
OL,15,FWhen was the last time we saw such
OL,16,Fconditions?
OL,18,FThe last few summers have been very
OL,19,Fmixed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
