OL,3,CWhat is a 'super plume' summer which
OL,4,Ccould push temperatures to 40C?
OL,6,FWe last saw this set up in 2022 - the
OL,7,Fyear of the historical 40C heatwave in
OL,8,FJuly, and in excess of 32C in June and
OL,9,Fclose to 35C in August. It was a
OL,10,Frecord-breakingly hot summer.
OL,12,FThe first half of summer 2023 also
OL,13,Ffollowed suit with June of that year
OL,14,Fbeing the hottest June on record - but
OL,15,Ffrom July of that year, the jet stream
OL,16,Fshifted, making for a disappointing
OL,17,Fremainder of the summer. It was
OL,18,Ffollowed by an unseasonable and
OL,19,Fprolonged heatwave during the first
OL,20,Fweek of September.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
