OL,3,CWhat is a 'super plume' summer which
OL,4,Ccould push temperatures to 40C?
OL,6,FLast year was unremarkable for much of
OL,7,Fthe summer, with temperatures below
OL,8,Faverage in June and July as the
OL,9,Fposition of the jet stream further
OL,10,Feast meant any hot continental air
OL,11,Fdrifted into southern Scandinavia. By
OL,12,Fthe first half of August, the
OL,13,Ftemperature recovered and peaked
OL,14,Faround 35C mid-month.
