OL,3,CWhat is a 'super plume' summer which
OL,4,Ccould push temperatures to 40C?
OL,6,FThe current positioning of the jet
OL,7,Fstream means we're on the cusp of a
OL,8,Fsoutherly airflow drawing in hot
OL,9,Fplumes of air from Europe, where
OL,10,Ftemperatures often exceed 40C.
OL,12,FWith the sun at its strongest this
OL,13,Ftime of year, it won't take much for
OL,14,Ftemperatures to soar.
OL,16,FWe have a higher-than-average chance
OL,17,Fof rising temperatures and hot, humid
OL,18,Fair this summer, and a high chance of
OL,19,Fheat waves in the coming weeks.
